section.section:
Of the 8 members:
Two shall be members of the scientific community in the State, one of whom shall be a geologist;
Three shall be members of the general public who have no financial interest in the waste disposal industry, at least one of whom has had a demonstrated involvement in environmental matters;
One shall be appointed from a list of three or more persons nominated by the Maryland Association of Counties;
One shall be appointed from a list of three or more persons nominated by the Maryland Chamber of Commerce; and
One shall be appointed from a list of three or more persons nominated by the Maryland Municipal League.
